sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin as Quan tri vien
    participant UI as Admin UI
    participant API as Admin API
    participant Store as Model Storage
    participant Registry as Model Registry
    participant Rasa as Rasa Runtime
    participant Log as Audit Log

    Admin->>UI: Upload model .tar.gz
    UI->>API: POST /admin/models
    API->>API: Validate file, version, checksum
    API->>Store: Luu model artifact
    Store-->>API: modelUri
    API->>Registry: Tao model version=PENDING
    API->>Rasa: Load/reload model
    alt Load thanh cong
        Rasa-->>API: Active model info
        API->>Registry: Cap nhat ACTIVE
        API->>Log: Ghi audit upload/run model
        API-->>UI: Thanh cong
    else Load loi
        Rasa-->>API: Error
        API->>Registry: Cap nhat FAILED
        API->>Log: Ghi audit loi
        API-->>UI: Tra loi loi
    end
